      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example has been mechanically vetted with a reinforced rear subframe and a recent VANOS system overhaul to maintain timing precision. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and chassis remain robust, providing a visceral, analog performance profile.",
