    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2018 Audi S5 Sportback is a stunning example of German engineering, blending high-performance capability with everyday utility. Finished in a deep Navarra Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and small surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather interior provides a striking contrast; the seats are supple and the cabin remains smoke-free, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a recent oil service. All electronics, including the Audi Virtual Cockpit and the premium Bang & Olufsen sound system, function perfectly. The car comes with a complete maintenance log, two keys, and tires with plenty of tread remaining. It is a reliable, spirited, and thoroughly maintained vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
